    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This technique allows the user to isolate and forcefully remove the effect of a single Genjutsu effect, so long as it can be dispelled. </p><p>You must first be aware that you or your target is under the effect of a Genjutsu. As part of the activation of this jutsu, make an Illusion Check at advantage vs the Save DC of the Genjutsu. On a success you free yourself or your target from the Genjutsu.</p>",
